## âœ… Usage Rules

1. **Mirror UI/UX patterns** â€” Copy layouts, spacing, interactions
2. **Apply Advyser colors** â€” Use our Teal (#14B8A6), not their colors
3. **One source per component** â€” Don't mix patterns from multiple sites
4. **Visit before building** â€” Always check the live site first
5. **Design system docs** â€” Wise has full docs at https://wise.design

---

